The 20th edition of the [[Central American and Caribbean Games]] was held in the city of [[Cartagena, Colombia]]. The tournament began on July 15 and ended on July 30.

==Host city==
*Main
**[[Cartagena, Colombia|Cartagena de Indias]]
*Other host cities
**[[Barranquilla|Barranquilla, Colombia]] (bowling, cycling, football/soccer, and shooting);
**[[Bogotá|Bogotá, Colombia]] (equestrian); 
**[[Mexico City|Mexico City, Mexico]] (rowing); and
**[[Santo Domingo|Santo Domingo, Dominican Republic]] (field hockey, modern pentathlon, racquetball and team handball).

