The '''Six Days of Berlin''' is a [[Six-day racing|six-day track cycling race]] held annually in [[Berlin]], [[Germany]]. The event was first held in 1909.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.memoire-du-cyclisme.eu/piste_6jours/6j_berlin.php |title=6 jours de Berlin (Allemagne) |publisher=Memoire-du-cyclisme.eu |date= |accessdate=2016-03-19}}</ref> [[Klaus Bugdahl]] holds the record of victories with nine.

